<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="de8568c4-d366-434c-9a4a-b7f14512d383" >

    <h3>How to create a news story:</h3> 
<p><strong>Important:</strong> Be sure to create an <a href="/content/ryerson/websupport/responsive-templates/archive-template.html">archive template</a> before you begin creating news pages. News pages must be created as child pages of a year/month archive.&nbsp;<br> </p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Once you have created your yearly &amp; monthly archives, navigate to the necessary month</li> 
 <li>Click <strong>New...</strong>&gt;<strong>New page</strong></li> 
 <li>Add descriptive Title and name (filename)<br> </li> 
 <li>Scroll down the template options and select <strong>News</strong></li> 
 <li>Click Create</li> 
</ul>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#de8568c4-d366-434c-9a4a-b7f14512d383");});</script></div>

				

				
