<p>The news template contains the following and embedded component containing</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Title&nbsp; - *The news story title becomes the default H1; the page title is still the Title added when the page was created</li> 
 <li>Thumbnail tab - add images to this tab that will appear in the grid view of a news list.</li> 
 <li>Sub Title</li> 
 <li>Link Name</li> 
 <li>Summary</li> 
 <li>Author</li> 
 <li>Date</li> 
 <li>Category</li> 
 <li>Tags</li> 
 <li>Embedded Text Component - use for body copy</li> 
 <li>Note: Other components can be added anywhere below the news release component<br> i.e. images, slideshows, layout components, etc.</li> 
 <li>Social sharing links can be displayed/or not displayed at the bottom of the release by enabling within the <a href="/content/ryerson/websupport/aem-basics/page-properties.html#tab-1484100597372-share-page-">page properties</a>, share tab.<br> </li> 
</ul>
    





